description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An excellent opportunity has arisen for a Clinical Nurse Specialist to join the Liaison Psychiatry Service as 1yrs Maternity Leave cover. You will a real passion for mental health care and be able to work in a challenging and dynamic environment.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Specialist Mental Health Nurse you will be committed to providing high quality Acute assessment in the Emergency Department and provide ongoing care and expertise to any patient admitted to our hospital with co-morbid Mental Health care needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Therefore we are seeking confident and accomplished practitioners to join our accredited service and join the shared vision of &#39;high quality care for all&#39;. The ideal candidate must have experience of acute (Crisis/Liaison) assessment at Band 6 level or above.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nik Munien, Service Manager for Mental Health&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: nik.munien@uhbw.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 0117 3429214&lt;/p&gt;
